Package server.Model

Class PersonalGoal

java.lang.Object
Observer.PersonalGoalObservable
server.Model.PersonalGoal
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class PersonalGoal extends PersonalGoalObservable implements Serializable
This Class represents the single PersonalGoal card as written in the game rules. The PersonalGoal cards give points to the Player that completes the schemes illustrated on the single cards. Every PersonalGoal possesses a unique scheme requiring that PlayableItemTiles with a specific Colour must be placed in specific positions in the Shelf in order to collect points. Have a look at MyShelfie RuleBook for further information
